{"id":292481,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/维权网-李淑兰、赵慧刚因从天安门路过被行政拘/","date":"2013-05-08T09:15:46Z","modified":"2013-05-08T09:15:46Z","title":"维权网 | 李淑兰、赵慧刚因从天安门路过被行政拘留（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员田静民报道）天津维权访民李淑兰、赵慧刚于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>途经天安门时，被查身份证带到天安门分局，随后被送往久敬庄。被地方政府押回天津后于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>以扰乱公共秩序为由将李淑兰行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>天、赵慧刚行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>李淑兰</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>岁的女儿于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span>被歹徒杀害。天津市公安局河西分局违法办案包庇罪犯，真凶在逃。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>李淑兰女儿全身有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">49</span><span>处伤，有录像为证，公安局认定是吸毒死亡，而毒品鉴定结果是（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">0.0036</span><span>毫克）与事实严重不符。李淑兰质疑毒品是自己女儿死后被嫌疑人注射于皮下，所以毒检结果是（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">0.0036</span><span>毫克）远不足以认定吸毒，更谈不上吸毒死亡。其公安局认定事实不清，法律依据不足。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>几年来李淑兰手持证据针对女儿的死因，天津、北京两地奔波上访告状，至今没有讨回一个说法。并于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日</span><span>因去中央政法委、中纪委等地上访维权，被天津市公安局打击报复拘留。今年两会</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>到天安门金水桥撒传单以示抗议。被天安门分局警察抓捕后拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天。到现在案件仍无说法。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>赵慧刚因天津市红桥区非法拆迁，得不到拆迁安置，至今一家人无家可归，多年上访问题得不到解决。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日</span><span>因去中央政法委、中纪委抗议政府腐败被天津公安非法拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天。今年两会</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>赵慧刚到天安门抗议腐败政府不予拆迁安置，从北京马家楼接回后，仍不予解决问题。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>赵慧刚只是从天安门经过，被天津市河北区政府、公安打击报复拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>现在李淑兰、赵慧刚已经被送往天津市拘留所执行拘留。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-KUvMGEgLUSM/UYoSC5JJY2I/AAAAAAAAhj8/Cdgdsn47JxA/s1600/P140113_1643%5B03%5D.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-KUvMGEgLUSM/UYoSC5JJY2I/AAAAAAAAhj8/Cdgdsn47JxA/s320/P140113_1643%5B03%5D.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-2IPPCUXzaFU/UYoSDbCVFdI/AAAAAAAAhkE/ChHx7VElzg0/s1600/P140113_1646.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-2IPPCUXzaFU/UYoSDbCVFdI/AAAAAAAAhkE/ChHx7VElzg0/s320/P140113_1646.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}